```plantuml
@startuml alanchn31_Movalytics-Data-Warehouse

actor User

User -> Airflow: Start ETL Process
Airflow -> BashOperator: Execute `load_staging_table.sh`
BashOperator -> Spark: Run Data Transformation
Spark -> S3: Read Data
Spark -> S3: Write Transformed Data
Spark -> Redshift: Load Data into Staging Tables

Airflow -> PostgresOperator: Run SQL Scripts
PostgresOperator -> Redshift: Upsert into Dimension Tables

Airflow -> DataQualityOperator: Perform Data Quality Checks
DataQualityOperator -> Redshift: Validate Data

Docker -> Airflow: Initialize Environment
Docker -> Airflow: Start Services

@enduml
```